    "We fine-tune a pretrained VGG-19 model as a feature extractor by applying our experiment dataset.",
    "This network model was created using the 19-layer variant of VGGNet.",
    "In this experiment, VGG-19 beat VGG-16 and other DL classifiers, such as AlexNet, ResNet-50, and Inception-V3 models as mentioned in Table 2.",
    "With values ranging from 256 to 512, four convolution layers are used to construct the following three subsections.",
    "Subsections of the convolutional layer are followed by pooling layers to reduce the trainable parameter."
